high_descs: walk forwards to the end of the room, then turn right and walk to the oven on the right side, turn left and face the counter on the left
grab the yellow knife off of the countertop
turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink on the left
slice up the green apple in the kitchen sink
turn to face the dishwasher on the left
open the bottom drawer to the left of the dish washer and put the knife inside
turn right to face the sink again
grab a apple slice out of the kitchen sink
turn left and walk over to the microwave ahead
place the apple slice inside of the microwave, cook it, then take it back out
turn around and walk to the end of the room, turn right and walk until you reach the fridge on the left, then face the fridge
place the apple slice inside of the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved apple slice inside of the fridge

high_descs: Walk forward to the wall, turn right, then turn left at the stove.
Pick up the knife next to the toaster.
Turn right twice, then left to face the sink.
Pick up the apple in the sink.
Turn left.
Open the bottom drawer and place the knife inside.
Turn right and face the sink.
Slice a quarter off of the apple.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the apple inside and warm the apple.
Turn around completely, walk forward, face the refrigerator on the right,
Open the refrigerator and place the apple slice on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed apple slice into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Go straight to the wall, turn right, go to the right of the stove top and face the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn right, bear right to the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into pieces.
Turn left to face the dishwasher.
Put the knife in the bottom drawer to the left of the dishwasher.
Turn right to the sink.
Take a piece of apple from the sink.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave and then take the apple from the microwave.
Turn around, go straight to the counter, turn right, go to the fridge on the left, face the fridge.
Put the apple on the upper shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple in a fridge.
